{ Corresponding squares are squares of reciprocal zugzwang.   We may speak of corresponding squares for kings, for kings with pawns, and with other material, we may speak of correspondence between any pairs of pieces.  The most commonly seen cases of corresponding squares are:   the opposition mined squares triangulation. }
1. -- *

