1... b4 2. c4 b3
{ 2...Ka5?  loses to  3.Kb3  Ka6  4.Kxb4  Ka7  5.Kb5  Kb7  6.a3!  Kc7  7.Ka6  Kc6  8.a4!  Kc7  9.Ka7  Kc6  10.Kb8! }
