{ 1.Kg1?  is wrong in view of  Bb6  2.Rh5+  Kg6  3.Rh2  Rxf2  4.Rxf2  a5  5.Kf1  Bxf2  6.Kxf2  a4  -+   Now  1.Kg3  Bb6  can be met with  2.Nd3! }
