{ Black to move and draw. } 1... Kb5
{ White, however, is better off than his opponent in that the loss of a pawn does not mean the loss of the game. }
2. Ke4 { But not  2.Kf6?  Kc4!  3.Ke6  Kc5  -+ } 2... Kc4 3. Ke3 Kxd5 4. Kd3
{ Draw. } *

