{ 1/17. Ravikumar-Nielsen, Esbjerg 1980  Black has a single way to a draw. }
1... Kb7
{ ∆ 2...dxc5.  All other moves lose.   1...dxc5?  2.b6  c4  3.a6  c3  4.a7+  Kb7  5.bxc7  +- and in case of @@StartFEN@@1k6/2p5/1P6/P1pP4/6p1/5pP1/5K2/8 b - - 0 2@@EndFEN@@  2...cxb6  3.a6  c4  4.d6  c3  5.d7  Kc7  6.a7  +-   1...Kc8?  2.a6!  ∆ 3.b6±   1...Ka7?  2.b6+  Kb7  3.bxc7  +- or  2...cxb6  3.cxd6  +-   1...Ka8?  (this was played in the actual game)  2.b6  Kb7  3.bxc7  Kxc7  4.cxd6+  Black resigned. }
2. a6+
{ 2.cxd6  cxd6=  and @@StartFEN@@8/1kp5/3p4/PPPP4/6p1/5pP1/5K2/8 w - - 1 2@@EndFEN@@  2.b6  cxb6!= }
2... Ka7 3. b6+ Kxa6 4. bxc7 Kb7 5. cxd6 Kc8 { Draw. } *

