1. Qb4+ Ka2 2. Qc3 Kb1 3. Qb3+ Ka1 4. Qe3 Kb1 5. Qd3 Kb2 6. Qe2 Ka1
{ But not  6...Kb1?  7.Kc4!  c1=Q+  8.Kb3  +- } *

