{ 1/20. A. Botokanov, 1985 } 1. Kf7
{ 1.Kf6?  Kg3  2.Kg5  Kxg2  3.Kxh4  Kxf3  would be bad, as Black's king would get to the queenside first. }
1... Kg3 2. Kg8 Kxg2 { 2...h3?  3.gxh3  Kxh3  4.Kf7  +- } 3. f4 h3 4. f5 h2 5.
f6 h1=Q 6. f7 { And there is no win for Black. } 6... Qh6 7. f8=Q Qxf8+ 8. Kxf8
Kf3 9. Ke7 Ke4 10. Kd6 Kd4 11. Kc6 Kc4 12. Kb6 Kxb4 13. Kxa6 Kc5 14. Kb7 b4 15.
a6 b3 16. a7 b2 17. a8=Q b1=Q+ { Diagram 16-10 } 18. Kc8
{ But not  18.Kc7?  Qh7+  and mate is forced. } 18... Qf5+ 19. Kb8 Qf4+ 20. Ka7
