{ 1/26. E. Dvizov, 1965 } 1. Kg6
{ 1.Kf6?  is only good enough for a draw:  1...Kg8!  2.g6  b3!  3.h6  b2  4.h7+  Kh8  5.g7+  Kxh7  6.Kf7  b1=Q  7.g8=Q+  Kh6= }
