[SetUp "1"]

{ N. Grigoriev, 1928    The direct  1.g4?  leads only to a draw:  1...b5  2.g5  b4  3.g6  b3+  4.Kc3  b2  5.g7  b1=Q  6.g8=Q+  Ka1!= }
1. Kc3 Ka3 2. Kc4 Ka4 3. g4 b5+ 4. Kd3
{ Here's the zigzag! The king returns to c2, while avoiding the pawn check. }
4... Ka3 5. g5 b4 6. g6 b3 7. g7 b2 8. Kc2 { Drawing the king into check. }
8... Ka2 9. g8=Q+ { White wins. } *

