Kf5 a5 4. e4+ { Diagram 16-17 } 4... Kc6
{ Black applies the Grigoriev zigzag. } 5. e5
{ Of course not  5.Ke5?  ∆ 6.Kd4  5...Kc5!  6.Kf6  a4  7.e5  a3  and Black promotes with check.   5.Kg6?  is also inaccurate in view of  5...a4  6.e5  Kd5!  7.Kf5  a3  8.e6  Kd6!  9.Kf6  a2  -+ }
5... a4 { 5...Kd7  6.Ke4= } 6. e6 a3 7. Kg6 { A similar zigzag saves White. }
