{ 1/34. N. Grigoriev, 1931 } 1. Kg3
{ The attack against the b7-pawn comes too late:  1.Kg5?  Kc2  2.Kf6  Kd3  3.Ke5  Kc4  4.Kd6  Kb5  5.Kc7  Ka6  ⨀  The only hope is to meet ...Kxb6 with Kb4. The trail should be blazed with awareness of the fact that the black king will try to out-shoulder its colleague. }
1... Kc2 2. Kf2 Kd3 3. Ke1 Kc4 4. Kd2 Kb5 5. Kc3 Kxb6 6. Kb4 { Draw. } *

