{ 1/36. A. Gerbstman, 1961 } 1. g7 { 1.b7?  Rc2+! } 1... Rc2+
{ Or  1...Rg2  2.b7  with the same result. } 2. Kb8 Rg2 3. b7 Rxg7 4. Ka8 Rg8+
{ 4...Rxb7  stalemate. } 5. b8=Q Rxb8+ 6. Kxb8 Kb6 { Diagram 16-19 } 7. Ka8
