{ Tragicomedies: Svacina − Müller, Vienna 1941    Black cannot capitalize on the active position of his king:  1...g4  2.Ke1  Kc2  3.Ke2=  Or @@StartFEN@@8/8/8/3p1ppp/3Pp3/3kP1P1/5PP1/3K4 b - - 0 1@@EndFEN@@  1...f4  2.gxf4  gxf4  3.exf4=  He thought up an amusing psychological trap: retreating his king instead. }
