1... Kf8 2. Qf5+ Qxf5 3. gxf5 Kg7 4. c4
{ A simpler way is  4.Kg4  Kf6  5.h6  +- or  4...Kh6  5.c4  and now in case of  5...Kg7  6.Kf3  ⨀ or  5...f3  6.Kxf3  Kxh5  7.Kg3  is good, too. And so is  7.f6  exf6  8.c5  +- @@StartFEN@@8/4p3/3p1P2/3P2pk/2P5/5K2/8/8 b - - 0 7@@EndFEN@@  7...Kg6  would not change the outcome either,  8.fxe7  Kf7  9.Kg4  Kxe7  10.Kxg5  +- }
