{ Tragicomedies: Winants − L. Hansen, Wijk aan Zee 1994  The position is drawn. Black tries one last chance: }
1... f3 2. gxf3+
{ The correct  2.g3!  f4  3.gxf4  Kxf4  leads to the 'normal,' i.e., drawn, position. }
2... Kh3 { White resigned. } 3. Ke3 Kg3 4. f4 Kg4 5. Ke2 Kxf4 6. Kf2
{ Black has two extra tempi  (even one would have been enough)  , since the pawn is above the c1-h6 diagonal and the king is in front of the pawn. }
