[SetUp "1"]

{ Tragicomedies: Bouaziz − Pomar, Siegen ol 1970    The proper array of the pawns would be g6/h7. So the win is:  1.h6!  Kf6  2.h7  Kg7  3.Kg4  Kh8  4.Kf5  e3  5.Kf6  e2  6.g7+  Kxh7  7.Kf7  . The immediate  3.Kf5  e3  4.Ke6  e2  5.h8=Q+  Kxh8  6.Kf7  +- was also possible. }
1. g7 { Is what White chose. } 1... Kf7 2. h6 Kg8 { Draw. } 3. Kf5
{ Or  3.Ke5  will be met by the same reply. } 3... Kf7
{ White cannot make progress. } *

