{ Tragicomedies: Chigorin − Tarrasch, Ostende 1905    The draw is obtained by constructing a stalemate refuge:  1.Kg4!  Ke4  2.g6!  h6  3.Kh5!=  and if  2...hxg6  3.fxg6  f5+  4.Kg5  f4  5.h5  f3  6.h6=  Just not  1.g6??  h5!  -+ }
1. gxf6 { This was the game continuation. } 1... gxf6 2. Kg4 Ke4 3. Kh3
{ Also insufficient was  3.Kh5  Kxf5  4.Kh6  when Black's simplest win is  4...Kg4  5.Kxh7  Kh5!  ,  (shouldering)  ,  but another possible win is @@StartFEN@@8/7p/5p1K/5k2/7P/8/8/8 b - - 1 4@@EndFEN@@  4...Ke6  5.Kxh7  f5  6.Kg6  f4  7.h5  f3  8.h6  f2  9.h7  f1=Q  10.h8=Q  Qf5+  with mate soon to follow. }
3... Kf4 { White resigned. } *

