{ Both Sides Have Reserve Tempi   In many cases, it is not hard to establish the number of reserve tempi available for both sides @@StartBracket@@as it was, for example in the endingKachiani-Maric, from @@StartBracket@@Diagram 1-174@@EndBracket@@. However, there are far more complex situations as well. }
1. -- *

