[White "Chapter 1 – Pawn Endgames III"]
[Black "Both Sides Have Reserve Tempi 1-191 EXTRA"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "8/1p5p/p4k2/8/4Pp2/7P/PP2K3/8 w - - 0 1"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ Šveida − Sika, Brno 1929  (analysis)   Now let's see what happens with White to move. }
1. Kf3 Ke5 2. h4 { But not  2.b4?  h6!  -+ } 2... a5 3. h5 a4
{ 3...h6  4.a4  +- } 4. h6 b6 { 4...a3  5.bxa3  b5  6.a4  bxa4  7.a3  +- } 5.
b4 axb3 { 5...a3  6.b5  +- } 6. axb3 b5 7. b4 Ke6
{ 7...Kf6  8.Kxf4  Kg6  9.Ke5!  Kxh6  10.Kf6  +- } 8. Kxf4 Kf6 9. e5+ Kg6 10.
Ke4 Kxh6 11. Kd5 Kg7 12. Kd6 h5 13. e6 { White wins. } *

