{ Tragicomedies: Draško − Vratonjic, Yugoslavia tt 1997 } 1. f4
{ An awful move! Without any need, White gives away two reserve tempi. The obvious drawing line was  1.Kd3  Kc5  2.Kc3  h5  3.h4  a6  4.f3  a5  5.f4= }
1... Kd6 2. Kd3 Kc5 3. Kc3 h5 4. Kb3 { 4.h4  a5  ⨀ -+ } 4... h4 5. Kc3 h3 6.
Kb3 a6
{ After  6...Kd4?  7.Kb4  a6  8.a5!  bxa5+  9.Kxa5  Kxc4  10.Kxa6  Kd4  White's king is just in time to get back to the kingside:  11.Kb5  Ke4  12.Kc4  Kxf5  13.Kd3  Kxf4  14.Ke2= }
7. a5 { 7.Kc3  a5  ⨀ -+ } 7... bxa5 8. Ka4 Kxc4 9. Kxa5 Kd4 10. Kxa6 Ke4 11.
Kb5 Kxf5 { White resigned. } *

