{ King in the Corner    Mate   If the defender's king is trapped in the corner, sometimes even a lone knight is able to mate.  A. Salvio, 1634  White to move wins @@StartSquare@@Ed. note:illustrated in the next variation@@EndSquare@@. But even with Black to move, the game lasts only a little longer. }
1... Kh1 { 1...g5  2.Nf6  g4  3.Nxg4+  Kh1  4.Kf1  ⨀  h2  5.Nf2# } 2. Nf6 Kh2
{ 2...h2  3.Ng4  g5  4.Ne3!  g4  5.Nf1  g3+  6.Nxg3#   2...g5  3.Ng4  ⨀  h2  4.Ne3! }
3. Ng4+ Kh1 4. Kf1 g5 5. Kf2 h2 6. Ne3 g4 7. Nf1 g3+ 8. Nxg3# *

