{ Tragicomedies: Trolldalen – Schüssler, Groningen ech jr 1975/76    With  1.Kc2  Nc4  and now stronger than  2.Bd2  Ke5  3.Be1!  Kxe4  , is  2.Bd8  Kd7  3.Kc3!  Nd6  4.Bh4  Nxe4+  5.Kd4  ,  when White would probably have drawn.   An even simpler route to the same end was  1.Kc3  Nc6  2.Kc4  Nxa5+  3.Kc5  ∆ 4.Kb6. }
