{ Tragicomedies: Trolldalen − Schüssler, Groningen ech jr 1975/76  (continued)     10...Nc7  11.Kc5  Kd3?  does not work:  12.Kb6  Kc4  13.Kxc7  Kb5  14.Kd6  Kxa5  15.Kc5=   Kubbel's solution was:  10...Nf6!!  11.Kc5  Nd7+  12.Kc6  Nb8+  13.Kb7  Kd5  14.Kxb8  Kc6!  (shouldering)  15.Kc8  Kb5  -+ }
1... Ne3+ 2. Kc5 Nc2 3. Kb6 Nb4 4. Kc5 Nd5 5. Kc4 Ke5 { 14...Nf6!! } 6. Kc5 Ke6
