{ Hernandez − Sula, Saloniki ol 1984 } 1. Nf8 Kxf8 2. Ke6
{ This knight sacrifice has allowed the king to invade the enemy camp. Black is in zugzwang. }
2... Ng7+ { On  2...Kg8  3.Ke7  decides. } 3. hxg7+ Kxg7 4. Kxd6 h5 5. Ke7 h4
6. d6 h3 7. d7 h2 8. d8=Q h1=Q 9. Qf8+ Kh7 10. Qf7+ Kh8 11. Qxf6+ Kh7
