9. Kf3
{ But this is a serious misstep. The white knight is placed unfortunately on c3 and needs to find a better post:   9.Nb5  g5  10.Kd3  Kf5  11.Nd6+=  and if  10...g4  11.hxg4  Nxg4  12.Ke4=  @@StartSquare@@Ed. note: trained in the previous variation.@@EndSquare@@ }
