[SetUp "1"]

{ Relocate the white king to d2, and it can reach the pawn in time to help it queen. }
1. Bh7 Kf7 2. Ke3 Kf6 3. Kf4
{ Everything we have said so far is elementary. Yet even strong players forget about these ideas surprisingly often, and make mistakes in the simplest positions. I had no difficulty finding examples for the “Tragicomedies” section of this chapter. }
