{ Tragicomedies: Maiwald – Bischoff, German ch Gladenbach 1997 } 1. Nxd5
{ White could have saved the game with this piece sacrifice.  After   1.Ne8?  Bc5+  2.Ke1  Ke4  White resigned, since the enemy king marches unhindered to g2. }
