{ Tragicomedies: Sax – Kovacevic, Sarajevo 1982 } 1. Bxh7
{ White has good chances for success. One very strong line is  1.Ke5!  Re1  2.Rc8  Re2  3.Rc7+  Kf8  4.Kd5  @@StartBracket@@∆ 5.Bxh7@@EndBracket@@. Another way of threatening the h7-pawn would be  1.Kg3!  But the immediate capture of this pawn is a terrible mistake.  1.Rxh7?  Kg8= }
