{ Actually, if he wishes, Black could even keep his h-pawn @@StartBracket@@which, in fact, has not the slightest value anyway@@EndBracket@@ by playing  11...h5  ,  instead of 11...Bf4,  12.b6   12.Kc7  Bf4+  13.Kc8  Be3=  12...Kd8  13.Kb7  Be3!=  , or  13.b7  Bf4  14.Kb6  Bb8!=  . }
