{ A mistake would be  1...Kg4?  2.Be7=  , and if  2...Kf3  @@StartBracket@@this position occurred in the game: White played Bc5?@@EndBracket@@, then  3.Kd2!  b2  4.Kc2  Kxe3  5.Kxb2  Kxf4  6.Kc3=  . }
