{ Hopeless is  2.hxg5  h4  3.Bd6  Bf5  4.g6  Bxg6  5.f5  Bxf5  6.Kxb3  Kg2  , or  3.f5  Bxf5  4.Kxb3  h3  5.Bd6  Kxe3  . }
2... d4+ { The b3-pawn must be defended as  2...Kg3?  3.Kxb3  is only drawn. }
3. exd4
{ An interesting sideline is  3.Bxd4  Kg3  4.g6  Kxh4  5.Kd2  and now rather than  5...Kg3  6.Be5+  Kg2  7.Bf6  , @@StartFEN@@8/8/4b1P1/7p/3B3k/1p2P3/3K4/8 b - - 1 5@@EndFEN@@  5...Kh3!  6.Ke2  Kg2!  7.Bf6  h4  , or  6.Bf6  h4  Threatening 7...Kg3.  7.Ke2  Kg2  -+  'Pants.' }
