[Result "*"]
[FEN "8/2K5/3P4/1B2k3/6b1/8/8/8 b - - 0 1"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ Black to move draws. } 1... Kd4
{ But not  1...Kd5?  2.Bd7  Bd1  3.Bc6+  and 4.d7. } 2. Bd7 Bd1 3. Bh3 Ba4 4.
Bg2 Kc5
{ Thus, if the weaker side's king cannot get in front of the pawn, then the basic defensive principle becomes:  king behind the king! }
