{ P. Heuäcker, 1930 } 1. Ba7 { 1.h7?  e4= } 1... Ba1 2. Kb1 Bc3 3. Kc2 Ba1 4.
Bd4 Bxd4 { 4...exd4  5.Kd3  +- } 5. Kd3 Bb2 6. Ke4 { White wins. } *

