3... Kf6 4. Kd2 { Or  4.Kd3  . } 4... Bf5 5. Bf3 Be4
{ The exchange of bishops on e4 or f3 leads to a drawn pawn ending.  Ed. note: the game continuation can be seen next → Diagram 6-31 }
