2. Bxe5 Kxe5 3. Kd3
{ If  3.c7  Bb7  4.Bd3  @@StartBracket@@∆ Bf5@@EndBracket@@, then  4...Kd6  5.Kd4  Bc8!   5...Kxc7  is less strong, but Black perhaps can survive after  6.Ke5  Bf3  7.Kf5  Kd6  8.Kxg5  Ke5  .  6.Bf5  Bxf5  7.gxf5  Kxc7  8.Ke5  Kd7  9.f6  g4  10.Kf4  Ke6  11.Kxg4  Kxf6=  , and if  6.Be2  Be6  or  6...Bd7= }
