[SetUp "1"]

{ If we move the position one file to the left, the diagonal grows shorter, and Black loses. }
1... Bd8 2. Nf4 Kf2 3. Ne6 Ba5 4. Ka6
{ These examples show us the  two basic techniques for promoting the pawn: driving the bishop off the diagonal, and interference. }
