1. Ke7 Kb2
{ 1...Kd2  2.Nd4!  Ke3  3.Ne6  Bg3  4.Ke8  Bh4  5.Nf8  Ke4  6.Ng6  ∆ 7.Ne7. }
2. Nd4 Ba5 3. Ne6 Kc3
{ Or  3...Bb4+  4.Kf6!  Bc3+  5.Kf5  Ba5  6.Ke4  Kb3  7.Kd5  ∆ Kc6, Nc7 +- } 4.
Kd6 Bb4+ 5. Nc5 Ba5 6. Nb7 Bb6 7. Kc6 { White wins. } *

