[Black "Cutting the King Off 8-2 EXTRA 1"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "7K/6R1/1k6/p7/8/8/8/8 b - - 0 1"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ With Black on move, the position is drawn. } 1... Kb5
{ Or  1...Kc5=  because cutting the king off along the fourth rank brings nothing.   @@StartSquare@@Ed. A likely scenario is  2.Rg4  a4  3.Kg7  a3  4.Kf6  a2  5.Rg1  Kb4  and the draw becomes obvious.@@EndSquare@@ }
*

