1... Kb2 { The correct move. } 2. Rb8+
{ 2.Rh2+  Kb3!  rather than  2...Kb1?  3.Kc3  +- } 2... Kc1 3. Ra8 Kb2 4. Kd2
a2 5. Rb8+ Ka1 { Draw. } *

