{ Shouldering } 1. Rh2+ Ka3
{ Black achieves a draw by not allowing the white king to approach the pawn.  1...Kb1?  is erroneous in view of  2.Kb3  a1=N+  3.Kc3  +- “Shouldering” is also often called “bodycheck.” }
*

