{ Fries-Nielsen – Plachetka, Rimavska Sobota 1991 } 1. Kc6
{ The game continuation.   1.Re8?  is no better:  1...h5  2.Rg8+  Kf3  3.Rh8  Kg4  4.Kc6  h4  5.Kd5  h3  6.Ke4  Kg3  7.Ke3  Kg2!  8.Rg8+  Kf1!=  or  8.Ke2  h2  9.Rg8+  Kh1!=  Black has to avoid @@StartFEN@@7R/8/8/8/8/4K1kp/8/8 b - - 3 7@@EndFEN@@  7...h2??  8.Rg8+  Kh3  9.Kf2!  h1=N+  10.Kf3  Kh2  11.Rg7  ⨀   White should have gained a tempo by means of the intermediate check  1.Rg2+!  @@StartSquare@@Ed. the line can be trained next → Diagram 8-12 EXTRA.@@EndSquare@@ }
1... h5 2. Kd5 h4 3. Ke4 h3 4. Ke3 Kg3 5. Re1 h2 6. Ke2 Kg2 7. Rh1 Kxh1 8. Kf1
{ Draw. } *

