{ Fries-Nielsen – Plachetka, Rimavska Sobota 1991  (analysis) } 1. Rg2+ Kf4
{ After  1...Kh3  2.Rg8  h5  3.Kc6  h4  4.Kd5  +-  The black king, pressed to the edge of the board, is placed extremely badly. }
2. Rh2 Kg5 3. Kc6 h5 4. Kd5 h4 5. Ke4 Kg4 6. Rg2+ Kh3 7. Rg8 { White wins. } *

