{ In a battle against two connected passed pawns,  the best position for the rook is behind the more advanced pawn. }
1. Rg6 Kd7 2. Rg4 g2 3. Rxg2 Ke6 4. Rg5
{ And White wins because the black king is cut off from the pawn along the fifth rank. }
