3. Kxe3 g3
{ As may be seen, White has gained a tempo rather than lost it, because his king is placed better on e3 than on e4. }
4. Rh8 Kh2 { 4...h2  5.Kf4= } 5. Rg8 g2 6. Kf2 { Draw. } *

