1... Kd8 2. Ra8+ Kc7 { Diagram 9-18 } 3. Re8 { 4.Kf6  Kd7!= } 3... Rh1
{ Rather than  4...Re2?  5.Kf7  Rh2  6.Rg8!  Rh7+  7.Rg7  Rh8  8.Ke7  Kc6  9.e6  Kc7  10.Rg1  +- }
4. Rg8 Re1 5. Rg2 Kd8
