{ Larsen misses his chance to punish his opponent for a grave positional error and allows him to employ the second defensive method in the Philidor position. The winning continuation was  5.Ke7!  Rh3  6.Ra4  @@StartBracket@@∆ Rc4+; Rd4@@EndBracket@@  6...Rh7+  7.Ke8  Rh8+  8.Kf7  +- }
