[SetUp "1"]

{ This is a typical case of an easy draw due to a frontal attack. } 1. Kb4
{ ∆ 2.c5+- } 1... Rb8+ 2. Ka5 Rc8
{ 2...Ra8+?  is erroneous in view of  3.Kb6  +- } 3. Kb5 Rb8+ 4. Ka6 Rc8 5. Rd4
Ke5 6. Rh4 Kd6 { Draw. } *

