{ Tragicomedies: Tal − I.Zaitsev, USSR ch tt, Riga 1968  (continued) } 1... Re5
2. Kd3 Kf5 3. Kd4
{ After  8.Rf1+  Kg4  9.Kd4   9.Rg1+  Kf3  10.Kd4  Ra5  -+  Both  9...Re2  10.Kd3  Rh2  or  10...Rg2  , and @@StartFEN@@8/8/8/4r1p1/3K2k1/8/8/5R2 b - - 6 4@@EndFEN@@  9...Ra5  10.Ke3  Ra3+  11.Ke2  Ra2+  12.Ke3  Kh3  -+ are strong. }
3... Re4+ 4. Kd3 g4 5. Rf1+
{ 10.Rg2  Rf4  11.Ke2  Kg5  12.Rf2  g3!  or  12.Rg1  Kh4  leads to the same result. }
5... Rf4 6. Ke2 { 11.Rg1  Kg5  12.Ke2  Kh4  -+ } 6... g3 7. Rxf4+ Kxf4 8. Ke1
Ke3 9. Kf1 Kf3 { Black wins. } *

