{ Tragicomedies: Khaunin − Fridman, Leningrad 1962 } 1... hxg3 2. hxg3
{ The winning continuation was  2.Kxg3!  Kh7  3.h4!  gxh4+  4.Kh3  Kg7  5.f4  and the f-pawn goes ahead with a decisive effect. }
2... g4+ 3. fxg4
{ A draw is inevitable, as White has only g-pawns @@StartBracket@@regardless of whether one or two@@EndBracket@@. }
