{ Tragicomedies: Vyzhmanavin – Lerner, USSR ch, Lvov 1984  In this drawn position, Black uses his last available trap, and unexpectedly succeeds. }
1... Ra3 2. Kd2 { Correct was, of course,  2.Kb2!  Rf3  3.Kc2  Kd5  4.Kd2= }
2... h2 3. Ke2 Ra1 { White resigned. } *

