{ A Far-Advanced Passed Pawn    Transition to a Rook vs. Pawns Endgame   It often happens that a passed pawn is so strong that the opponent must inevitably give a rook away for it. In such cases, one should take into account and know well the methods we have learned from studying rook versus pawns endgames. }
1. -- *

[Event "?"]
