{ Tragicomedies: Tarrasch − Blümich, Breslau 1925  Tarrasch resigned! He saw that his king was cut off from his own pawn along the fourth rank, while the attempt to advance the pawn }
1. h6 { would have been met by } 1... Rb6 2. Rh5 a2 3. h7 Rb8
{ The grandmaster had completely forgotten the possibility of deflecting the black rook from the 8th rank: }
4. Rb5+ Rxb5 5. h8=Q+ { Draw. } *

