{ Or  13.Rc7  . But  13.Rd7?  is incorrect on account of  13...Ke5  ⨀= } 3...
Ke5 { 13...Kd5  14.Kf5  +- } 4. Rd7
{ Now it is Black who has fallen into zugzwang. } 4... Ke4 5. Rd1 Kf3 6. Rf1+
Ke2 7. Rf7 Ke3 8. Kf5 { White wins. } *

