{ 9/17. Mednis-Djukic, Nis 1977  (analysis)   Grandmaster Karsten Müller has proven that even after }
1. b7 Rf8 { White can still win. } 2. Ra2 { Instead of  4.Rc2? } 2... Rf2 3.
Ra4 Rf8 4. Kc6 Kxg2 5. Ra8 Rf6+ 6. Kc5 Rf5+ 7. Kc4 Rf4+ 8. Kc3 Rf3+ 9. Kd2 Rb3
10. b8=Q { White wins. } *

