{ 9/19 Stein – Vaganian  (variation)  , Vrnjacka Banya 1971 } 1... gxf5
{ It looks like things are hopeless for Black, as the white king is about to come in and kick the black rook away from the position in front of the pawn. But Black has one last chance: stalemate! }
2. gxf5 Kh5 3. Kb8 h6 { 3...Ra5  first also draws. } 4. Kxa7
{ Stalemate. This idea was found by WGM Irina Kryukova.  Diagrams 16-86 and 16-87 have been intentionally omitted. }
