{ V.Kantorovich 1989/J.Steckner 2003, et al @@StartSquare@@Ed. continued from Diagram 9-168h@@EndSquare@@     In addition to  4.Ra8  , Black must also reckon with: }
4. Kb6 Rb2+ 5. Kc7 { Diagram 9-172 } 5... Ra2
{ In the variation  5...Rc2+?  6.Kd8!  Rxf2  7.Re7+  Kf6  8.Rc7  Ra2  9.a7  Kf5  10.Kc8  Kg4  11.Rc4+  Kg3  12.Kb7  he does not manage to save himself:  12...Rb2+   12...f5  13.Rc6!  Rxa7+  14.Kxa7  Kxh4  15.Kb6  +-  13.Kc6  Ra2  14.Kb6  f5  15.Rc8!  +- }
6. Kb8
