{ Tragicomedies: Lerner − Dorfman, USSR ch  (1)  , Tashkent 1980  (continued)   @@StartSquare@@Ed. Diagram 9-184 and Diagram 9-183 have been intentionally reversed in order to make for a smoother training experience.@@EndSquare@@ }
1. Rf2
{ Excellent! The rook prevents the shouldering maneuver that was possible after  14.Kb7 ?  Kf6  15.Kc6  Ke5!=  For the sake of restricting the enemy king, White does not begrudge a vital tempo. }
1... Kg6 2. Kb7 g4 3. Kc6 Kg5 4. Kd5 g3 5. Rf8 Kg4 6. Ke4 { Black resigned. } *

