{ An illogical move, as it makes sense only in connection with the capture on h4, but Black cannot take this pawn.   Both  8...Kg6  and  8...Ra2  would have been better. But, even with the saved tempo, it is too late now for Black to save the game. @@StartSquare@@Ed. analysis →Diagram 9-185j@@EndSquare@@ }
