1. Rc7 Re8 2. b7 { 7.Rc3  Rb8  8.Rb3  Ke6= } 2... Rb8 3. Kd3 Kf5
{ Diagram 9-197 } 4. Rxf7+
{ Or  9.Ke3  Kg4  10.Kf2  f6  11.Rc4+  Kf5!  12.Rb4  g5  13.Kf3  Ke5  14.Rb5+  Kd6  15.Ke4   15.hxg5  fxg5  16.Rxg5  Rxb7  17.Rxh5  Ke6=  15...Kc6  16.Rb1  gxh4  17.gxh4  Rxb7  18.Rxb7  Kxb7  19.Kf5  Kc7= }
