{ Tragicomedies: Heinemann − Zelbel, German Bundesliga 2014  (continued)   Black is in a fatal zugzwang. He must move his king to the back rank, after which White gains a crucial tempo, because Black cannot take the pawn on f4. }
14... Kg8 15. Kd3 Kg7
{ 15...Rxf4  16.Rb7  Ra4  17.a7  and Black is paralyzed while White brings the king to  b8  . And in case of @@StartFEN@@6k1/1R3p2/P5p1/6Pp/5r1P/3K4/8/8 b - - 1 16@@EndFEN@@  16...Rxh4  17.a7  Ra4  18.Rb8+  is why White needed to force the king to go to  g8  . }
16. Kc3 Rxf4 17. Rb7 Rxh4 18. Rb4 Rh3+ 19. Kb2 Rh2+ 20. Ka3
