6... Ra2 7. f3 Ra1 8. Kf4 Kd6 9. Ke4 Re1+ 10. Kd4 Rd1+ 11. Kc3 Rc1+ 12. Kb2
{ Diagram 9-214a } 12... Rg1 13. Rb5 Rg2+ 14. Kc3 Rg3
