{ 1...g4+?  2.Kf4  is hopeless. In the game, Black resigned after a single move:  1...gxh4?  2.gxh4  , in view of  2...Rg7  3.a4  @@StartBracket@@∆ @@StartFEN@@8/6r1/1p2p3/3kPp1p/P2P3P/2R1PK2/8/8 w - - 0 4@@EndFEN@@  4.a5  bxa5  5.Rc5#  @@EndBracket@@ or  2...Ra8  3.Rc7  Rxa3  4.Rd7+  . Instead of being persecuted, the black king could have become a dangerous attacking piece! }
