1... g5 2. Rxh7 Rxa2 3. Rh6+ Ke5 4. Rxc6 Ke4 5. Rxc5 f4
{ Preparing an umbrella against checks along the f-file. } 6. exf4 Kf3 7. h3
Ra1+
{ Draw. White has four @@StartBracket@@!@@EndBracket@@ extra pawns in the final position. }
