4... Ke4 { If  4...Ke2  , then  5.Nc5  Kd2  6.Kb2!  , and the pawn goes. } 5.
Kb4 { Of course not  5.Nc5+??  Kd4  6.Nxb3+  Kc4  -+ } 5... Kd4 6. Nb2 Rh3 7.
Na4 Kd3 8. Kxb3 Kd4+ { Draw. } *

