{ 10/1. Zahrab, IX century } 1. Re3 Ng1 2. Kf5
{ The mined squares for the kings are f4 and d4.   The premature  2.Kf4?  Kd4  ⨀  misses the win:  3.Re1  Nh3+  4.Kg3  Ng5  5.Kf4  Nh3+= }
