{ After  25.g5??  Black wins either by  25...Rg3+  ∆ 26...Rxg5, or by  25...Kxg5  26.Ne4+  Kf4  27.Nf2  Rd2  ⨀  And @@StartFEN@@8/8/5N2/8/5kP1/3r4/6K1/8 w - - 1 21@@EndFEN@@  25.Kh2?  is a mistake, in view of  25...Rd6  26.g5  Rd8!  -+ }
