{ White gets nothing from  2.Re5  Nf5  3.h3  g4!  But now, after @@StartFEN@@8/1p1k4/p2np3/1P1p2pp/3P4/1P1K2P1/7P/4R3 b - - 0 2@@EndFEN@@  2...Nxb5  , White will play  3.Re5  +-, while taking on b5 with a pawn opens up the a-file. }
