{ The only way to victory is to utilize the bad position of the bishop.   After  2.Kg6?  Kf8  the black king slips away from the dangerous corner. }
2... Be1
{ 2...Bg3  3.Rg4+  , or  2...Bf2  3.Kg6  Kf8  4.Rf4+  , and if  2...Bd8  3.Ra8  , while after  2...Be7  3.Kg6  +- }
3. Kg6 Kf8 4. Rf4+ { ∆ 5.Re4 +- } *

