{ 11/3. J. Vancura, 1924 } 1. Kg5
{ But of course not  1.Kh6?  Be4!  2.Ra7  Bb7!=  And not  1.Ra7?  Be4+!  2.Kh6  Bb7  3.Ra4  Be4!=  Black must avoid @@StartFEN@@7k/R6P/6K1/8/8/8/8/7b b - - 1 1@@EndFEN@@  1...Bb7??  2.Kh6  ⨀ }
1... Bg2
{ 1...Kxh7  2.Rh4+  and if @@StartFEN@@7k/7P/8/6K1/R7/8/8/7b b - - 1 1@@EndFEN@@  1...Bc6  2.Rc4  Bd5  3.Rd4  ∆ 4.Kh6. }
