Rg3 Bc1 16. Rd3+ Kc4 17. Rd7
{ Endgame handbooks suggest  17.Ke4  followed by driving the black king back one more file, but this is already superfluous: he may go after the h6-pawn immediately. }
17... Bg5 18. Kg6 Kc5 19. Rh7 Kd6 20. Rxh6 { White wins. } *

