Kh1 Kh3 34. Bc5
{ As we know,  34.Kg1!  Rg2+  35.Kf1  would have led to a draw. } 34... Ra1+
35. Bg1 Kg4 36. Kh2 Ra2+ 37. Kh1 Kg3 38. Bc5 Rh2+ 39. Kg1 Rd2 40. Kh1 h3
{ White resigned. } *

