{ Y. Averbakh, 1962  (continued) } 6... Ka1
{ The queen cannot be captured because of stalemate, while a king's retreat loses the pawn: }
7. Kd4 Qb4+ 8. Qc4
{ 8.Kd5  Qb7+  and if @@StartFEN@@8/6P1/8/8/1q1K4/3Q4/8/k7 w - - 14 8@@EndFEN@@  8.Ke5  Qe7+ }
8... Qd2+ 9. Kc5 Qg5+ { Draw. } *

