{ Tragicomedies: Chigorin – Schlechter, Ostende 1905 } 1... Qc7+
{ The last trap in this totally hopeless position. } 2. Qb6+
{ After  2.b6  or  2.Kb4  , Black would have had only one option – to capitulate. }
2... Ka8
{ If White takes the queen Black is stalemated, otherwise a sort of perpetual check happens: }
3. Ka6 Qc8+ 4. Ka5 Qc7 { Draw. } *

