{ Larsen − Keres, San Antonio 1972  (continued) } 15. Kf4
{ White should have accepted a drawn outcome:  15.Kh3  . The attempt to play for a win turns out to be playing for a loss. }
15... Qh2+ 16. Kg5 { 16.Ke3  is still sufficient to draw. } 16... Qg3
{ There is no satisfactory defense from  17.--  hxg4  . } 17. Qe3 hxg4 18. Qf4
Qxf3 19. Qxg4 Qe3+ 20. Qf4 Qe2 21. Qg3 Qb5+ 22. Kf4 Qf5+ 23. Ke3 Qxf6
