Qc2+ { With the idea of  12.Kd5  Qa2+  , White continues: } 12. Ke5 Qc3+
{ 12...Qb2+  13.Qd4! } 13. Kd5 Qc4+ 14. Kd6 Qb4+ 15. Kc6 Qc3+ 16. Kb7
{ Maróczy’s plan to use the b5-pawn as an umbrella succeeds after all.  Diagrams 12-30 and 12-31 have been intentionally omitted. }
