{ Black loses in spite of the fact that his king occupies a 'regular' position in front of the pawn. }
1... Rh6 2. Qd7
{ Zugzwang. If  2...Rf6  then  3.Qd8+  Kf7  4.Qxf6+  gxf6+  5.Kh6  is decisive. }
