{ Rook and Knight vs. Rook   A draw with a rook against a rook and a knight is not a difficult procedure. Even when your king is confined to the edge of the board, you can usually slip away from mating threats @@StartBracket@@sometimes with the help of stalemate@@EndBracket@@. }
1. -- *

