{ van der Weide − Marovic, Amsterdam 1967  (continued)   Dražen Marovic finds the only road to victory. }
1... Bg2 2. Rd8+ Ke3 3. Re8+ Be4
{ The matter has been reduced toPhilidor's position. } 4. Rg8 Rc7 5. Rd8 Rc1+
6. Rd1 Rc2 7. Rd8 { Somewhat more stubborn, as we know, is  12.Rd7  . } 7...
Rg2 8. Rf8 Bg6 9. Rf6 Bd3 10. Re6+ Be4 11. Rf6 Re2+ 12. Kf1 Rc2 13. Kg1 Rg2+
14. Kf1 Rg5 15. Ke1 Bf5 { White resigned. } *

