{ Timman − Lutz, Wijk aan Zee 1995  (continued) } 28. Rf4+ Kg3 29. Ke3 Kh3
{ 29...Rg8 } 30. Rf5 Rg3+ { 30...Kg4 } 31. Kf2 Rg2+ 32. Kf1 Rc2
{ A retreat of the rook  32...Rg6  , preparing  33.--  Kg4  or  33.--  Kg3  , was simpler. }
33. Rg5 Rc4 34. Be5 Kh4 35. Rg8 Re4 { 35...Rg4! } 36. Bg3+ Kh5 37. Kf2 Ra4
