1... Rb4 2. Kd5 Rb1 3. g5 { White has no better plan to follow. } 3... hxg5 4.
hxg5 fxg5 5. Nxg5+ Kg8 6. Ne6 Rd1 7. Ke4 { 7.Nxg7  Rxd4+= } 7... Kf7 8. Ng5+
