{ King's Activity   "In the middlegame the king is a mere spectator; in the endgame on the other hand − one of the major participants," Nimzovitch wrote in My System. Make use of every available moment to improve your king's placement − its active position is often decisive for the outcome of the fight. }
1. -- *

