{ Tragicomedies: Svidler – Anand, Dos Hermanas 1999  In this position a draw was agreed. Meanwhile, White had a forced win: }
1. Kxd4 Nb5+ 2. Kc5 Nxa7 3. Kb6
{ Chasing after two birds! By pursuing the knight, White wants to bring the king closer to his pawns. }
3... Nc8+ 4. Kc7 Na7 { If  4...Ne7  , then  5.h7  Kg7  6.f6+! } 5. Kd7 Nb5
{ Or  5...Kf6  6.h7  Kg7  7.f6+  Kxh7  8.f7  Kg7  9.Ke8!  +- } 6. h7 Kg7 7. f6+
Kxh7 8. f7 Kg7 9. Ke7 { White wins. } *

