{ 15/1. N. Grigoriev, 1932 } 1. Kf5
{ Shouldering!   1.h5?  is wrong in view of  1...Kg4  2.h3+  Kh4  ⨀ The same holds for both @@StartFEN@@8/6p1/6K1/8/7P/5k2/7P/8 w - - 0 1@@EndFEN@@  1.h3?  Kg3  2.h5  Kh4  ⨀= And  1.Kg5?  Kg2  2.h5  Kh3  ⨀  3.Kg6  Kg4!= }
1... Kg2 2. h5 Kh3 { If  2...Kf3  then the same reply follows. } 3. Kg5
{ Zugzwang. } 3... Kxh2 4. Kg6 { White wins. } *

