1. Ke3 Bxe2
{ 1...Bh3?  2.Kf2=  or  1...Nh3?  2.Be8=  and if @@StartFEN@@8/3p4/6B1/8/k7/4K3/4P3/5bn1 b - - 1 1@@EndFEN@@  1...Bg2 ?  2.Bc2+  and 3.Kf2=. }
2. Bf5 d6
{ Both  2...Bb5  3.Kf2  Ne2  4.Bxd7  and @@StartFEN@@8/3p4/8/5B2/k7/4K3/4b3/6n1 b - - 1 2@@EndFEN@@  2...d5  3.Be6  Bc4  4.Kf2  Ne2  5.Bxd5  lead to an immediate draw. }
3. Kd4 { 4.Kd5 is threatened. } 3... Bf3 4. Be4 Ne2+
