{ Another way to a mate was  11.Bf6+  Kf7  12.Qe7+  Kg8  13.Qe8+  Kh7  14.Qh8# }
6... Kg8 7. Qe8+
{ Black resigned on account of  12...Kh7  13.Qg6+  Kh8  14.Bf6#  Or @@StartFEN@@4Q1k1/8/8/5PB1/8/1KP5/PP4q1/7q b - - 6 7@@EndFEN@@  12...Kg7  13.f6+  Kh7  14.Qf7+  Kh8  15.Qg7# }
