{ 15/37. A. Troitsky, 1910 } 1. Rc2+
{ The line  1.Kd2?  a1=Q  2.Nd3+  Ka2!   Rather than  2...Kb1?  3.Rc1+  Ka2  4.Nb4+  Kb2  5.Rxa1  Kxa1  6.Kc1  ⨀  6...a2  7.Nc2#  3.Nc1+  Kb1!  4.Rb3+  Qb2+  only leads to a draw. }
